All Implemented Interfaces:
RasterDataSource
public class PackagedRasterDataSource
extends StreamRasterDataSource

A raster data source that uses the map bundled in the /res/raw/ folder as a source. The request are generated based on resourceTemplate that may contain various tags. The following tags are supported: zoom, x, y, xflipped, yflipped, quadkey For example if, if resourceTemplate = "t{zoom}_{x}_{y}.png", then the result (for root tile) will be "/res/raw/t0_0_0.png".
